df8 = df7.merge(df7, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df9 = stadium[(stadium['name'] != 's') | (stadium['stadium_id'] >= 1) | (stadium['name'] != 's') & (stadium['stadium_id'] < 9) | (stadium['city'] == 'l') | (stadium['city'].str.startswith('r'))]
df10 = df8.merge(df9, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df11 = stadium[(stadium['capacity'] > 89186) & (stadium['name'] != 's') & (stadium['location'].str.startswith('n')) & (stadium['name'] != 's') | (stadium['capacity'] != 62606)]
df12 = df10.merge(df11, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df13 = df12.groupby(by=['location', 'year_built', 'city', 'name']).agg('min', numeric_only=True)

df1 = match[(match['team2_id'] == 't') | (match['score_team1'] <= 1) | (match['match_date'] < '2022-12-18') & (match['score_team2'] < 2) | (match['team2_id'].str.startswith('t')) & (match['team2_id'].str.startswith('t'))]
df2 = df1[['team1_id', 'score_team2', 'match_date', 'match_id', 'duration_minutes', 'stadium_id', 'score_team1', 'team2_id', 'attendance', 'round']]
df3 = stadium[(stadium['capacity'] < 41430) & (stadium['city'] != 'l') | (stadium['stadium_id'] != 9) & (stadium['capacity'] == 51503)]
df4 = df2.merge(df3, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df5 = df4.merge(df4, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df6 = stadium[['capacity', 'name', 'stadium_id', 'year_built', 'location', 'city']]
df7 = df5.merge(df6, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df8 = stadium[['capacity', 'name', 'stadium_id', 'year_built', 'location', 'city']]
df9 = df7.merge(df8, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df10 = stadium[(stadium['stadium_id'] != 10) & (stadium['city'].str.startswith('l')) | (stadium['location'] != 'w') | (stadium['stadium_id'] > 2) | (stadium['year_built'] <= 1980)]
df11 = df10[['capacity', 'stadium_id', 'year_built', 'location', 'city']]
df12 = df9.merge(df11, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df13 = df12.groupby(by=['stadium_id', 'location', 'year_built']).agg('min', numeric_only=True)

df1 = match[(match['team2_id'] != 't') & (match['round'] != 'semi-final') | (match['match_id'] == 28) & (match['score_team1'] != 4)]
df2 = df1[['stadium_id', 'match_id', 'score_team2']]
df3 = stadium[(stadium['capacity'] <= 50660) | (stadium['stadium_id'] >= 8) & (stadium['city'] != 'a') & (stadium['capacity'] > 41756)]
df4 = df3[['city', 'name', 'capacity', 'stadium_id', 'location']]
df5 = df2.merge(df4, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df6 = stadium[(stadium['stadium_id'] < 7) | (stadium['location'] == 'c') & (stadium['year_built'] >= 1976) & (stadium['capacity'] == 53720) | (stadium['city'] == 'a') & (stadium['name'].str.startswith('s'))]
df7 = df6[['name', 'stadium_id', 'location', 'year_built']]
df8 = df5.merge(df7, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df9 = stadium[['city', 'name', 'capacity', 'stadium_id', 'location', 'year_built']]
df10 = df8.merge(df9, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df11 = stadium[['city', 'capacity', 'stadium_id', 'year_built']]
df12 = df10.merge(df11, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df13 = stadium[(stadium['city'] != 'l') & (stadium['city'] != 'd') & (stadium['location'].str.startswith('n')) & (stadium['capacity'] < 73244) & (stadium['city'].str.startswith('l'))]
df14 = df13[['capacity', 'stadium_id', 'name']]
df15 = df12.merge(df14, left_on='stadium_id', right_on='stadium_id')
df16 = df15.groupby(by=['capacity', 'name']).agg('max', numeric_only=True)
